The water retentivity of the cellulose based fiber of high water-retentive is 200% or more.


The term "water retentivity" herein means a value represented by the following formula 2;


W (%)=+(D-C)/C} * 100  (Formula 2)

The absorbency and water retentivity of the viscose rayon-polyacrylate based fiber F of high water retentivity of the present invention, thus produced, are 700% or more and 200% or more, respectively.


The term absorbency herein means the value represented by the following formula 1;


V (%)=+(B-A)/A} * X 100  (Formula 1)
